text.section:
To register, the following shall be submitted:
The person's name and address;
The address where the waste tires are to be accumulated or transferred;
A statement of the purpose for accumulating, transporting, or processing the waste tires;
A statement of the maximum number of waste tires to be accumulated, transported, or processed, and their passenger tire equivalents, as calculated under KRS 224.50-862;
The rate at which waste tires are to be accumulated, transported, or processed;
A certification stating that the person has read and understood the requirements of the waste tire program and will comply with those requirements;
Financial assurance to pay for closure and corrective action as required by KRS 224.50-864 and 224.50-866; and
A disclosure statement required by KRS 224.40-330(2).
